high_descs: Turn left, proceed across room to stove.
Remove pot from bottom left burner.
Turn around, proceed across room to refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put pot on second shelf down, close refrigerator.  Close door, wait five seconds, open refrigerator.  Remove pot, close refrigerator door.
Turn around, proceed to table on right.  Turn right, proceed to table.
Place pot on table in front of coffee maker, to the right of tomato.
anns.task_desc: Move pot from stove to refrigerator, chill pot, move pot to counter.

high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the oven.
Pick up the large metal pan that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Put the metal pan in the fridge for a couple seconds then take it out and close the fridge door.
Walk over to the small white table with the coffee maker on it.
Put the chilled metal pan on the white table in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on a white table.

high_descs: turn left, walk forward to counter, turn right, take a step, turn left to face the stove
pick up the pan that is on the stove
open fridge, put pan in, close fridge, wait a minute, take pan out of fridge
turn around, take a few steps, turn right to face the table
put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: put a chilled pan on the table
